videoDetails.Title: The among us song played in Desmos
videoDetails.Description:
Since you can't play multiple graphs at the same time I had to edit them to play at the same time.

If you want to see the graph here it is: https://www.desmos.com/calculator/nixzh3xzyr

And yes, I am aware that there is a missing beat (meaning one measure only has 1 beat instead of 2). I realized that after I added all the beats in, and it would've taken a while to fix it.

Join my discord server to post your suggestions!
https://discord.gg/hpFQMRR4h8
